  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Lost Penguin is a Sokoban-style cozy puzzle game. The player moves the penguin on a 2D grid to reach the goals by strategically planning the route, connecting with friends, interacting with eggs, gates, teleports, enemies, and more. The rules are simple yet the combinations create infinite depth.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You move a penguin on 2D tiles. Moving drains energy. Energy exhaustion immobilizes the player. Recharge areas refill energy. A level can have multi-penguin goals that require the player to connect with other penguins to form a group.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984360/extras/a4de65bded21692a2ed1ecf3f6ea792e.poster.avif?t=1733247127\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984360/extras/a4de65bded21692a2ed1ecf3f6ea792e.webm?t=1733247127\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984360/extras/a4de65bded21692a2ed1ecf3f6ea792e.mp4?t=1733247127\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Eggs can be hatched to create a new penguin, or pushed away to change the environment. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984360/extras/64d1530e6aac45be7405f3a6eb3cb58d.poster.avif?t=1733247127\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984360/extras/64d1530e6aac45be7405f3a6eb3cb58d.webm?t=1733247127\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984360/extras/64d1530e6aac45be7405f3a6eb3cb58d.mp4?t=1733247127\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984360/extras/fd498614a0982d5fdfabca97d941cd22.poster.avif?t=1733247127\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984360/extras/fd498614a0982d5fdfabca97d941cd22.webm?t=1733247127\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984360/extras/fd498614a0982d5fdfabca97d941cd22.mp4?t=1733247127\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Movable snow blocks work like a switch that changes the path dynamically.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984360/extras/f436fd2d52eb25d619380800d96d520a.poster.avif?t=1733247127\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984360/extras/f436fd2d52eb25d619380800d96d520a.webm?t=1733247127\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984360/extras/f436fd2d52eb25d619380800d96d520a.mp4?t=1733247127\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Predators are dangerous, but sometimes can be surprisingly helpful.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984360/extras/80c2bbcb1bb7ae8feaa8a3066bb3053a.poster.avif?t=1733247127\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984360/extras/80c2bbcb1bb7ae8feaa8a3066bb3053a.webm?t=1733247127\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984360/extras/80c2bbcb1bb7ae8feaa8a3066bb3053a.mp4?t=1733247127\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Send a love letter to another penguin to remotely synchronize movements.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984360/extras/a77ff7a7eb860a2a6d942485d8303e79.poster.avif?t=1733247127\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984360/extras/a77ff7a7eb860a2a6d942485d8303e79.webm?t=1733247127\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984360/extras/a77ff7a7eb860a2a6d942485d8303e79.mp4?t=1733247127\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >70 hand-crafted levels. Each level presents a new problem that requires a unique solution.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Lost Penguin is a Sokoban-style cozy puzzle game. The player moves the penguin on a 2D grid to reach the goals by strategically planning the route, connecting with friends, interacting with eggs, gates, teleports, enemies, and more. The rules are simple yet the combinations create infinite depth.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You move a penguin on 2D tiles. Moving drains energy. Energy exhaustion immobilizes the player. Recharge areas refill energy. A level can have multi-penguin goals that require the player to connect with other penguins to form a group.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984360/extras/a4de65bded21692a2ed1ecf3f6ea792e.poster.avif?t=1733247127\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984360/extras/a4de65bded21692a2ed1ecf3f6ea792e.webm?t=1733247127\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984360/extras/a4de65bded21692a2ed1ecf3f6ea792e.mp4?t=1733247127\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Eggs can be hatched to create a new penguin, or pushed away to change the environment. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984360/extras/64d1530e6aac45be7405f3a6eb3cb58d.poster.avif?t=1733247127\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2984360/extras/64d1530e6aac45be7405f3a6eb3cb58d.webm?t=1733247127\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic